{"id": "1490612742439174144", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "我觉得最新这版最好看诶，气质符合了，而且对比之下第一版人体怪怪的，头好像要掉了，第三版更准确吧", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:22:52.043000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:24:27.584000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1479475299237494888", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "把阿拉克涅的立绘改回去", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1490612820478398525", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是我支持游戏内给开关选项喜欢哪版用哪版", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:23:10.649000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1479475299237494888", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "把阿拉克涅的立绘改回去", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1490613010522439700", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "白荆回廊就有，有个角色公测改了立绘画风，玩家可以自选用哪版，虽然大部分人还是选了新版", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:23:55.959000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1479475299237494888", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "把阿拉克涅的立绘改回去", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1490613584122613832", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "😂 我还希望他们也改一下卡拉布呢，那个人体才是问题特别大。当时b站wb评论我还记得说过卡拉布丑要求改。。白川泊川画卡拉布明显摸鱼了。。根本不是白川正常的水平。万一卡拉布也有人喜欢旧版的，大不了卡拉布也给个开关自选免得吵架", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:26:12.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-06T07:32:58.562000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1479475299237494888", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "把阿拉克涅的立绘改回去", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
